What you need to know:

During her visit to Kenya in 1988, former British Prime Minister Margaret Thatcher toured Vihiga County and used the Shem-Kivuye-Chekombero-Mululu road, which locals have since renamed Thatcher Road.Thatcher Road is the only living testimony of the former British Premier’s tour that awoke the sleepy villages of Kivuye, Chekombero and Mululu 32 years ago.